			<li>We are dedicated to building a network of compassionate individuals and organizations committed to making a tangible difference in the fight against hunger. By working together, we amplify our impact and create lasting change in our communities.</li>
			<li>Through education and advocacy, we strive to raise awareness about the causes and consequences of food waste and hunger. Our goal is to inspire action and empower individuals to take part in our mission.</li>
